Jeremy Hawkins (amụrụ n'August 8, 1991) nke a maara dị ka JHawk ma ọ bụ JHawb Productions, bụ ónyé America na-emepụta ihe ndekọ, ónyé na-ede egwu, na ónyé na-eme ihe nkiri si Los Angeles, California

A maara ya màkà ịbụ Onye ọsụ ụzọ nke Jerkin 'Movement, na-enweta ọtụtụ iri nde echiche na iyi, na-enye aka nke ukwuu na ihe ịga nke ọma nke ọtụtụ ndị na-ese ihe na Los Angeles. Hawkins bụ ónyé a maara nke ọma maka ịmepụta egwu Rej3ctz "Cat Daddy" na 2011 nke ruru Number 77 na Hot R&B / Hip-Hop Songs ma nweta asambodo Platinum n'onwe ya.
JHawk tolitere n'ogige ntụrụndụ nke Los Angeles, Leimert Park
Ma nne na nna bụ ndị na-agụ egwú, nne bụ ónyé na-agụ egwu n'ógbè ahụ na nna bụ onye na'ọtụtụ ngwá egwú

Ọ bụkwa nwa nwanne nna nke The Chambers Brothers, (Time Has Come Today), na-ahụkarị ndị otu ahụ na-emegharị ma na-eme ihe ngosi màkà nne nne ha. N'oge na-adịghị anya mgbe ọ natara ngwanrọ mbụ ya nke na-eme ka egwu Hip Hop EJay site n'aka nna ya, ọ malitere ịkụ egwu mgbè ọ dị afọ iri na otu ma chọọ ịghọ onye na-emepụta egwu
N'ikwu okwu na Killerhiphop's Quez, "E wepụtara abụ mbụ m na ịntanetị mgbe m dị ihe dị ka 15-16, m na-esikwa m ike kemgbe ahụ".
